# Project Overview

## Structure
```
apps/
  opik-backend/       # Java 21, Dropwizard, MySQL, ClickHouse
  opik-frontend/      # React, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind
  opik-documentation/ # Fern docs
sdks/
  python/             # Python 3.8+, Pydantic, httpx
  typescript/         # Node 18+, TypeScript, Zod
  opik_optimizer/     # Python optimization SDK
deployment/           # Docker Compose, Helm charts
tests_end_to_end/     # Playwright E2E tests
```

## Quick Commands
| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Start dev | `./scripts/dev-runner.sh --restart` |
| Start (no rebuild) | `./scripts/dev-runner.sh --start` |
| Stop | `./scripts/dev-runner.sh --stop` |
| Build BE | `./scripts/dev-runner.sh --build-be` |
| Build FE | `./scripts/dev-runner.sh --build-fe` |
| Docker full | `./opik.sh --build --port-mapping` |

## URLs (dev mode)
- Frontend: `http://localhost:5174`
- Backend: `http://localhost:8080`
- Swagger: `http://localhost:8080/swagger`

